    <entry>
      <title>MATLAB-04初阶绘图</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/09/MATLAB-04%E5%88%9D%E9%98%B6%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/09/MATLAB-04%E5%88%9D%E9%98%B6%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用-plot-函数绘制图线">使用 <code>plot()</code>函数绘制图线</h2><p>在MATLAB中，使用 <code>plot()</code> 函数绘制图线，其语法为：</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">plot</span>(x,y,LineSpec)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>各参数含义如下：</p><ul><li><code>x</code>: 图线上点的x坐标</li><li><code>y</code>: 图线上点的y坐标</li><li><code>Linespec</code>:图线的线条设定,三个指定线型,标记符号和颜色的设定符组成一个字符串,设定符不区分先后.具体细节请参考<a href="https://www.mathworks.com/help/matlab/ref/linespec.html">MATLABDocumentation</a>.</li></ul><table><colgroup><col style="width: 18%" /><col style="width: 22%" /><col style="width: 18%" /><col style="width: 11%" /><col style="width: 18%" /><col style="width: 11%" /></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th>线型设定符</th><th>线型</th><th>标记设定符</th><th>标记</th><th>颜色设定符</th><th>颜色</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td><code>-</code></td><td>实线（默认）</td><td><code>o</code></td><td>圆圈</td><td><code>y</code></td><td>黄色</td></tr><tr class="even"><td><code>--</code></td><td>虚线</td><td><code>+</code></td><td>加号</td><td><code>m</code></td><td>品红色</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td><code>:</code></td><td>点线</td><td><code>*</code></td><td>星号</td><td><code>c</code></td><td>青蓝色</td></tr><tr class="even"><td><code>-.</code></td><td>点划线</td><td><code>.</code></td><td>点</td><td><code>r</code></td><td>红色</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td><code>x</code></td><td>叉号</td><td><code>g</code></td><td>绿色</td></tr><tr class="even"><td></td><td></td><td><code>s</code></td><td>方形</td><td><code>b</code></td><td>蓝色</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td><code>d</code></td><td>菱形</td><td><code>w</code></td><td>白色</td></tr><tr class="even"><td></td><td></td><td><code>^</code></td><td>上三角</td><td><code>k</code></td><td>黑色</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td><code>v</code></td><td>下三角</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr class="even"><td></td><td></td><td><code>&gt;</code></td><td>右三角</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td><code>&lt;</code></td><td>左三角</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr class="even"><td></td><td></td><td><code>p</code></td><td>五角形</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td></td><td></td><td><code>h</code></td><td>六角形</td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="hold-onoff">hold on/off</h2><p>Use hold on to have both plots in one figure</p><p>MATLAB在绘制图形时，会清除窗口内之前的图形，使用该指令可以保持图窗</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">hold</span> on </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">plot</span>(<span class="built_in">cos</span>(<span class="number">0</span>:<span class="built_in">pi</span>/<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">2</span>*<span class="built_in">pi</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">plot</span>(<span class="built_in">sin</span>(<span class="number">0</span>:<span class="built_in">pi</span>/<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">2</span>*<span class="built_in">pi</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">hold</span> off</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
