    <entry>
      <title>MATLAB-03变量和档案存取</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/09/MATLAB-03%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%A1%A3%E6%A1%88%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/09/MATLAB-03%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%A1%A3%E6%A1%88%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="matlab-variables-and-data-access">MATLAB Variables and Dataaccess</h1><p>[[MATLAB3~MATLAB variable.png]]</p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th>数值类型</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>double</td><td>双精度浮点数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>single</td><td>单精度浮点数</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>int8</td><td>8位带符号整数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>int16</td><td>16位带符号整数</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>int32</td><td>32位带符号整数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>int64</td><td>64位带符号整数</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>uint8</td><td>8位无符号整数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>uint16</td><td>16位无符号整数</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>uint32</td><td>32位无符号整数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>uint64</td><td>64位无符号整数</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="variables">Variables</h2><h3 id="characterchar">Character(char)</h3><ul><li>A character is represented in ASCII using a numeric code between 0to 255</li><li>Create a character or a string by putting them into a pair ofapostrophe</li><li>Use <code>uint16()</code> to convert a char to its ASCII code</li></ul><h3 id="string">String</h3><ul><li>An array collects characters:<ul><li><code>s1 = 'Example';</code></li><li><code>s2 = 'String'</code></li></ul></li><li>String concatenation:<ul><li><code>s3 = [s1 s2];</code></li><li><code>s4 = [s1; s2];</code><ul><li>Error: Dimension of matries being concatenated are notconsistent</li><li><code>s5 = [s1; s1]</code><ul><li>It works well</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="logic-operations-and-assignments">Logic Operations andAssignments</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str = <span class="string">&#x27;aardvark&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> == str<span class="comment">% return  [1 1 0 0 0 1 0 0]</span></span><br><span class="line">str(str == <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>) = <span class="string">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span><span class="comment">% return  &#x27;ZZrdvZrk&#x27;  replace &#x27;a&#x27; with &#x27;Z&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="structure">Structure</h3><ul><li>A method of storing heterogeneous data</li><li>Structures contain arrays called fields</li><li>Students assignment grades:</li></ul><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">student.name = <span class="string">&#x27;John Doe&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">student.id = <span class="string">&#x27;jdo2@sfu.ca&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">student.number =<span class="number">301073268</span>;</span><br><span class="line">student.grade = [<span class="number">100</span> <span class="number">75</span> <span class="number">73</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">95</span> <span class="number">91</span> <span class="number">85.5</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">100</span> <span class="number">98</span> <span class="number">72</span> ]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">student</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr class="header"><th>函数名</th><th>函数作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>struct</td><td>创建结构体</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>struct2cell</td><td>将结构体转换为元胞数组</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>cell2struct</td><td>将元胞数组转换为结构体</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>isstruct</td><td>判断某变量是否是结构体</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>structfun</td><td>对结构体的每个字段都应用某函数</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>fieldnames</td><td>获取结构体的所有字段名</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>isfield</td><td>判断结构体是否包含某字段</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>getfield</td><td>获取结构体某字段的值</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>setfield</td><td>为结构体中的某字段赋值</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>rmfield</td><td>删除结构体中的某字段</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>orderfields</td><td>为结构体字段排序</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p>[!example]</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><code>rmfield(student,'id')</code></p></blockquote><p>Nesting Structure</p><h3 id="cell-array">Cell Array</h3><ul><li>Another method of storing heterogeneous data</li><li>Similar to matrix but each entry contains different type ofdata</li><li>Declared using <code>&#123; &#125;</code></li><li>The two following expressions are the same<ul><li>A{m, n} = element;</li><li>A(m ,n) ={element};</li></ul></li><li>Each entry in a cell array hold s a pointer to a data structure</li><li>Different cells of the same cell array can point to different typesof data structures</li></ul><h4 id="access-cell-array">Access Cell Array</h4><ul><li>有两种方式访问元胞数组中的数据,分别是:<strong>单元索引</strong><code>()</code>，和<strong>数组索引</strong><code>&#123;&#125;</code><ul><li>使用单元索引(),我们得到的是一个子元胞数组.</li><li>使用内容索引{},我们得到的是元胞数组对应区域中的内容.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>)=&#123;[<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">4</span> <span class="number">3</span>; <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">8</span>; <span class="number">7</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">9</span>]&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">A(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>)=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;Anne Smith&#x27;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">A(<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">1</span>)=&#123;<span class="number">3</span>+<span class="number">7</span><span class="built_in">i</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">A(<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">2</span>)=&#123;-<span class="built_in">pi</span>:<span class="built_in">pi</span>:<span class="built_in">pi</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">A(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment">% 1*1 cell array  &#123;&#x27;Anne Smith&#x27;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">A&#123;<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>&#125; <span class="comment">% 1*10 char array &#x27;Anne Smith&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="matrix2cell-and-num2cell">matrix2cell and num2cell</h4><p>use <code>help</code> or <code>doc</code></p><h4 id="multidimensional-array">Multidimensional Array</h4><p>[[MATLAB3~multidimensional array.png]]</p><h4 id="cat">cat()</h4><p>使用cat函数可以在指定维度上对元胞数组进行拼接(concatenation)</p><p>[[MATLAB3~cat.png]]</p><h4 id="reshape">reshape()</h4><p>Create a matrix B from the matrix A below using reshape():</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A = &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;James Bond&#x27;</span>, [<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span>;<span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">4</span>;<span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">6</span>]; <span class="built_in">pi</span>, <span class="built_in">magic</span>(<span class="number">5</span>)&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C = <span class="built_in">reshape</span>(A,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">4</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A = [<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span>;<span class="number">4</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line">B = <span class="built_in">reshape</span>(A,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span class="math display">\[A = \left(\begin{array}{ccc} 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3\\ 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow B = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 1 &amp; 5\\ 4&amp; 3\\ 2 &amp; 6 \end{array}\right)\]</span></p><h2 id="file-access">File Access</h2><h3 id="mat-format">MAT format</h3><p>MATLAB工作区里的数据可以以 <code>.mat</code> 格式保存在文件中，使用<code>save</code> 函数将数据存入文件，使用 <code>load</code>函数从文件中读取数据</p><ul><li><code>save</code> 函数的语法如下：<ul><li><code>save(filename， variables)</code> 将变量<code>variables</code> 以二进制形式存入文件中</li><li><code>save(filename, variables, '-ascii')</code>将变量以文本形式存入文件中</li></ul></li><li><code>load</code> 函数的语法如下：<ul><li><code>load(filename)</code>从二进制形式文件中读取数据.</li><li><code>load(filename,'-ascii')</code>从文本形式文件中读取数据.</li></ul></li></ul><p>其中参数filename和variables都是字符串格式,若不指定variables参数,则将当前工作区内所有变量存入文件中.</p><blockquote><p>复杂的数据格式,如struct和cell,不支持以二进制格式存储.</p></blockquote><h3 id="excel-file">Excel File</h3><ul><li>读取Excel文件：<code>[num,txt,raw] = xlsread(filename,sheet,xlRange)</code><ul><li>自动去掉文字部分</li></ul></li><li>写入Excel的语法:<code>xlswrite(filename,A,sheet,xlRange)</code></li><li>同时读取文本和数字可以使用以下操作：<code>[Score Header] = xlsread('score.xlsx')</code></li></ul><h3 id="low-level-file-io-functions">Low-level File I/O Functions</h3><p>同C语言的文件I/O</p><p>使用 <code>type filename</code> 可以打印出文本的内容</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
