      <title>MATLAB-01基本操作和矩阵输入</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/09/MATLAB-01%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/09/MATLAB-01%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>不声明时默认的类型时double</p><h2 id="special-variables-and-constants">Special Variables andConstants</h2><ul><li><p>ans</p></li><li><p>i, j : complex number</p></li><li><p>Inf : ∞</p></li><li><p>eps : epsilon, 2.2204e-16</p></li><li><p>NaN : not a number</p></li><li><p>pi : π</p></li><li><p>To list Keywords:</p><ul><li>&gt;&gt; iskeyword</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="arrayvector-and-matrix">Array(Vector and Matrix)</h2><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Row vector:</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; a = [<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Column vector:</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; b = [<span class="number">1</span>; <span class="number">2</span>; <span class="number">3</span>; <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Try:</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; a*b</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; b*a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Output:</p><p><span class="math display">\[a*b=30\]</span></p><p><span class="math display">\[b*a =\left(\begin{array}{cccc}1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4\\2 &amp; 4 &amp; 6 &amp; 8\\3 &amp; 6 &amp; 9 &amp; 12\\4 &amp; 8 &amp; 12 &amp; 16\end{array}\right)\]</span></p><p>用空格(space)隔开行元素，用分号(semicolon)隔开不同的列元素</p><h3 id="array-indexing">Array Indexing</h3><ol type="1"><li>A(n): 取出矩阵的第n个元素（MATLAB采用列优先）</li><li>A(row, column): 取出矩阵第row行第column列的元素</li><li>A(Matrix or Vector):使用矩阵或者向量的值索引，返回一个按原方式排列的矩阵或向量</li><li>A(row vector, column vector):使用第一个向量作为行数，第二个向量作为列数，取二者交叉元素</li></ol><h3 id="colon-operator">Colon Operator</h3><p>create a array: <code>start: step: stop</code>, different from pyton:<code>range(start, stop, step)</code></p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; B = <span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; B = <span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; B = [<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">5</span>; <span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">3</span>:<span class="number">15</span>; <span class="number">-2</span>:<span class="number">0.5</span>:<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; str = <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>:<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="string">&#x27;z&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用冒号运算符清空矩阵中的某一行或者某一列：</p><p><code>A(3,:) = []</code>: 清空第三行，这里的[ ]表示empty</p><h3 id="array-concatenation">Array Concatenation</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A = [<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span>; <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">4</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; B = [<span class="number">9</span> <span class="number">9</span>; <span class="number">9</span> <span class="number">9</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; C = [A B]</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; D = [A;B]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Output:</p><p><span class="math display">\[A = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 1 &amp; 2\\ 3 &amp; 4 \end{array}\right)\\B = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 9 &amp; 9\\ 9 &amp; 9 \end{array}\right)\\C = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 9 &amp; 9\\ 3 &amp; 4&amp; 9 &amp; 9 \end{array}\right)\\D = \left(\begin{array}{cc} 1 &amp; 2\\ 3 &amp; 4\\ 9 &amp; 9\\ 9 &amp;9 \end{array}\right)\]</span></p><h3 id="array-manipulation">Array Manipulation</h3><p>Operators on array: <code>+</code> <code>-</code> <code>*</code><code>/</code> <code>^</code> <code>.</code> <code>'</code></p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A+B    <span class="comment">%对应的每个元素(entry)相加</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A*B    <span class="comment">%矩阵做乘法</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A.*B   <span class="comment">%矩阵的对应元素(entry)相乘</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A/B    <span class="comment">%A乘以B的逆矩阵(inverse matirx)</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A/B    <span class="comment">%A和B的每个对应元素相除</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; A&#x27;     <span class="comment">%转置(transpose) B矩阵</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：当a为数值时，A.*a和A*a相同，A.\a和A\a相同，但是A^a和A.^a不同</p><h3 id="some-special-matrix">Some Special Matrix</h3><ul><li><code>linspace()</code>: linearly spaced vectors<ul><li><code>linspace(start, stop, number)</code></li></ul></li><li><code>eys()</code>: n*n identity matrix</li><li><code>zeros(n1, n2)</code>: n1*n2 zero matrix</li><li><code>ones(n1, n2)</code>: n1*n2 matrix with every entry as 1</li><li><code>diag()</code>: diagonal matrix</li><li><code>rand()</code>: uniformly distributed random numbers</li></ul><h3 id="some-matrix-function">Some Matrix Function</h3><p>column width function</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">max</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">max</span>(<span class="built_in">max</span>(A))</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">min</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; sum(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">mean</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">sort</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">sortrows</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">size</span>(A)     <span class="comment">% return the dimension of matirx as vector [row colomn]</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">length</span>(A)   <span class="comment">% return the biggest dimension number of matirx</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">find</span>(A)     <span class="comment">% find(matrix == key) will return the index of key(column vector if there are duplicate entries)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>For example:</p>$$<span class="math display">\[\begin{aligned}M = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 16 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 13\\ 5 &amp; 11&amp; 10 &amp; 8\\ 9 &amp; 7 &amp; 6 &amp; 12\\ 4 &amp; 14 &amp; 15&amp; 1 \end{array}\right)\\\\\max(M) = \left(\begin{array}{cccc}16 &amp; 14 &amp; 15 &amp;13\end{array} \right)\\\\\max(\max(M)) = 16\\\\\mathrm{sum}(M)=\left(\begin{array}{cccc} 34 &amp; 34 &amp; 34 &amp; 34\end{array}\right)\\\\\mathrm{sum}(\mathrm{sum}) = 136\end{aligned}\]</span><p>$$</p><p>The <strong>difference</strong> between <code>sort</code> and<code>sortrows</code>:</p><p>sort函数会将每一个row的内部进行排序后输出，而sortrows函数则只会比较第一个row，它将每一个column视为整体进行排序：</p><p>For example:</p>$$<span class="math display">\[\begin{aligned}M = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 16 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 13\\ 5 &amp; 11&amp; 10 &amp; 8\\ 9 &amp; 7 &amp; 6 &amp; 12\\ 4 &amp; 14 &amp; 15&amp; 1 \end{array}\right)\\\\\mathrm{sort}(M) = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 4 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 1\\5 &amp; 7 &amp; 6 &amp; 8\\ 9 &amp; 11 &amp; 10 &amp; 12\\ 16 &amp; 14&amp; 15 &amp; 13 \end{array}\right)\\\\\mathrm{sortrows}(M) = \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 4 &amp; 14 &amp; 15&amp; 1\\ 5 &amp; 11 &amp; 10 &amp; 8\\ 9 &amp; 7 &amp; 6 &amp; 12\\ 16&amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 13 \end{array}\right)\end{aligned}\]</span><p>$$</p><h2 id="words">Words</h2><ol type="1"><li>even number: 偶数</li><li>odd number:奇数</li><li>increment</li><li>concat: 合并</li><li>concatenate: 连接，联系的</li><li>semicolon: 分号</li><li><h2 id="broken-key-points">Broken Key Points</h2></li></ol><span class="math display">\[e^{x}= 1+ \frac{x}{1!}+ \frac{x^{2}}{2!}+ \frac{x^{3}}{3!}+...\]</span> $$<span class="math display">\[\begin{aligned}\end{aligned}\]</span><p>$$</p><ol type="1"><li>use <code>latex(variable)</code> to convert matlab expression toLaTeX expression.</li><li><code>rem(a,b)</code> will return the remainder of a/b.</li><li><code>prod(array)</code> will return the product of elements in thearray</li><li><code>clear</code> will delete all varibles in workspace, and<code>clear varible name</code> will only delete specific varible inworkspace</li><li>use <code>tic</code> to start the timer, and use <code>toc</code> tostop the timer. <code>tic</code> and <code>toc</code> appear in pairs tocalculate the time the program runs.</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
