      <title>MATLAB-06数值计算</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/09/MATLAB-06%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/09/MATLAB-06%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="多项式">多项式</h2><h3id="使用matlab表示多项式polynomials">使用MATLAB表示多项式（Polynomials）</h3><p>在MATLAB中，多项式可以用向量表示（rowvectors），第一位为多项式最高次项系数，最后一项为常数项</p><blockquote><p>[!example]</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><span class="math display">\[f(x) = x^{3}-2x-5\]</span> 可以用向量 <code>p = [1 0 -2 -5]</code> 表示</p></blockquote><h3 id="多项式求值polyval">多项式求值：<code>polyval()</code></h3><p>使用 <code>polyval(p,x)</code> 计算多项式 <code>p</code> 在<code>x</code> 每个点处的值</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = [<span class="number">9</span> <span class="number">-5</span> <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">7</span>]; x = <span class="number">-2</span>:<span class="number">0.01</span>:<span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">f = polyval(a,x);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">plot</span>(x,f,<span class="string">&#x27;LineWidth&#x27;</span>,<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="多项式的乘法conv">多项式的乘法：<code>conv()</code></h3><p>使用<code>conv(p1, p2)</code>函数可以对两个向量p1和p2进行卷积相乘,用于计算多项式的乘法.</p><p>例如多项式 <span class="math inline">\(f(x) =(x^2+1)(2x+7)\)</span>，可用下式计算：</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p = conv([<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">1</span>], [<span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">7</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% return p = [2 7 2 7]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3id="多项式的微分derivativepolyder">多项式的微分（derivative）：<code>polyder()</code></h3><p>使用 <code>polyder(p)</code>函数可以计算<strong>多项式</strong>的导数</p><p>配合 <code>polyvar()</code> 可以计算出指定点的微分</p><h3id="多项式的积分integrationpolyint">多项式的积分（Integration）：<code>polyint()</code></h3><p>使用 <code>polyint(p, k)</code>函数可以计算多项式p的积分,积分结果的常数项设为k。返回值为多项式的向量</p><p>k省略时常数项为0</p><blockquote><p>[!example] <span class="math display">\[f(x) =5x^4-2x^2+1\]</span></p></blockquote><p><code>p = polyint([5 0 -2 0 1], 3)</code></p><p>得到 <code>p = [1 0 -0.6667 0 1 3]</code>,表示计算得到如下积分:</p><p><span class="math display">\[\int f(x) dx=x^{5}-0.6667x^3+x+3\]</span></p><h2 id="非线性表达式">非线性表达式</h2><h3 id="数值微分">数值微分</h3><h4 id="求差分diffxn">求差分：<code>diff(x,n)</code></h4><p>使用<code>diff(X, n)</code>计算向量<code>X</code>的<code>n</code>阶差分,<code>n</code>默认为<code>1</code>.<figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = [<span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">diff(x);<span class="comment">% 得到 [1 3 -3 -1]</span></span><br><span class="line">diff(x,<span class="number">1</span>);<span class="comment">% 得到 [1 3 -3 -1] </span></span><br><span class="line">diff(x,<span class="number">2</span>);<span class="comment">% 得到 [2 -6 2] 相当于对diff(x,1)的返回值进行差分运算</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h4 id="求导数diffy.diffx">求导数：<code>diff(y)./diff(x)</code></h4><p>使用导数的定义：</p><p><span class="math display">\[f^{&#39;}(x) = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{f(x_0+h)-f(x_0)}{h}\]</span></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
